you should put the text which you want to scroll within the <marquee> </marquee>.


15)what are the tags that are used to sepration of text ?
<br> :used to seperate the line of text.
<p>: This contains the text in the form of a new paragraph.


16)what is diff betwn div and span ?
->The <div> tag defines a division or a section in an HTML document. The <div> tag is used as a container for HTML elements - which is then styled with CSS 
or manipulated with JavaScript

 In HTML, the span tag is a generic inline container element. Span tags usually wrap sections of text for styling purposes or for adding attributes to a section 
 of text without creating a new line of content.
 
 17)what is <!Doctype html> ?
->All HTML documents must start with a <!DOCTYPE> declaration.
The declaration is not an HTML tag. It is an "information" to the browser about what document type to expect.
 
 18)Is the <!Doctype html> tag consirdred as an html tag?
 ->No not a html tag there are many types of html such as html4.0,xhtml3.0.
 doxtype s used to instruct the web browser about the html page.
 
 
 19)how to make a picture of background image of aa web page ?
