27)In how many types of css can be included in html ?
->
a)inline css = Thies is used to styling small context.
b)external stylesheet = this is used to style is applied to many diff pages.
each page must be link to style sheet using link tag.
link tag goes in to the head section. 
  <head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href ="mystyle.css">
  </head>
c)Internal stylesheet
This is used when single document has unique style.
so the internal stylesheet needs to put in the head section in html page.
So internal stylesheet has to put in the head section in html page by using style tag.






